        the below items aren't a huge deal and can be done after finishing the other tabs
        * Think about just having personal notes and not generalized flagset notes
        * Style dialog better
        * dialog component? adding in personal notes, that'll be three different dialogs and attendent methods all here, which
does not feel great.
        * fix alignment with + buttons on those rows
    */
}